@tdurden83
 I was really upset that they cut the big Tyrion battle scene from Season 1 Episode 9. This was supposed to be a defining moment for everyone's favourite dwarf and changes the character ever so slightly in the TV show. The producers apparently ran out of money towards the end of the season and could not afford the battle choosing to instead add filler content which created certain deviations in the story line that are now becoming apparent. 

I heard that the overall story arcs will be solid though and there is no real way for them to stay true to such epic books so a pretty decent effort overall I think. Keep in mind this is an entire universe they have had to make from scratch! Maybe one day they will remake stories like this exactly as described in books.
